+
+// error-pattern: are too big for the current ABI
+
+struct S32<T> {
+    v0: T,
+    v1: T,
+    v2: T,
+    v3: T,
+    v4: T,
+    v5: T,
+    v6: T,
+    v7: T,
+    v8: T,
+    u9: T,
+    v10: T,
+    v11: T,
+    v12: T,
+    v13: T,
+    v14: T,
+    v15: T,
+    v16: T,
+    v17: T,
+    v18: T,
+    v19: T,
+    v20: T,
+    v21: T,
+    v22: T,
+    v23: T,
+    v24: T,
+    u25: T,
+    v26: T,
+    v27: T,
+    v28: T,
+    v29: T,
+    v30: T,
+    v31: T,
+}
+
+struct S1k<T> { val: S32<S32<T>> }
+
+struct S1M<T> { val: S1k<S1k<T>> }
+
+fn main() {
+    let fat: Option<S1M<S1M<S1M<u32>>>> = None;
+}
